{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"iddb4d8f7d-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s627"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"627"},"text":"§ 627.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" State taxation","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Any corporation organized under the provisions of this subchapter shall be subject to tax by the State within which its home office is located in the same manner and to the same extent as other corporations organized under the laws of that State which are transacting a similar character of business. The shares of stock in such corporation shall also be subject to tax as the personal property of the owners or holders thereof in the same manner and to the same extent as the shares of stock in similar State corporations.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"iddb4d8f7e-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1913-12-23/ch6/s25A"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1913, ch. 6, § 25A","children":[],"tail":" (par.), formerly § 25(a), as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1919-12-24/ch18"},"text":"Dec. 24, 1919, ch. 18","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/41/378"},"text":"41 Stat. 378","children":[],"tail":"; renumbered § 25A, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/242/tI/s142/e/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–242, title I, § 142(e)(2)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1991-12-19"},"text":"Dec. 19, 1991","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/105/2281"},"text":"105 Stat. 2281","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"iddb4d8f7f-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"iddb4d8f80-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"iddb4d8f81-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This subchapter, referred to in text, was in the original “this section”, meaning section 25A of act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1913-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1913","children":[],"tail":", which is classified to this subchapter (§ 611 et seq.)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"iddb4d8f82-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section is comprised of par. 19 (undesignated) of section 25A of act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1913-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1913","children":[],"tail":", which comprises this subchapter. For complete classification of section 25A of this Act, see Codification note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s611"},"text":"section 611 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
